  "lyrics": [
    {
      "time": 26.699,
      "time_str": "00:26.699",
      "text": "If the hero never comes to you",
      "translation": "如果那个英雄从未来到你身边"
    },
    {
      "time": 32.437,
      "time_str": "00:32.437",
      "text": "If you need someone you're feeling blue",
      "translation": "如果你在忧郁时需要一个人"
    },
    {
      "time": 38.331,
      "time_str": "00:38.331",
      "text": "If you wait for love and you're alone",
      "translation": "如果你孤单并渴求一份爱情"
    },
    {
      "time": 44.198,
      "time_str": "00:44.198",
      "text": "If you call your friends nobody's home",
      "translation": "如果你的朋友都不在身边"
    },
    {
      "time": 50.157,
      "time_str": "00:50.157",
      "text": "You can run away but you can't hide",
      "translation": "你可以离开但你不能逃避"
    },
    {
      "time": 56.059,
      "time_str": "00:56.059",
      "text": "Through a storm and through a lonely night",
      "translation": "穿越暴风雨和那个孤单的夜晚"
    },
    {
      "time": 61.927,
      "time_str": "01:01.927",
      "text": "Then I'll show you there's a destiny",
      "translation": "然后我就会将这命运展现给你"
    },
    {
      "time": 66.586,
      "time_str": "01:06.586",
      "text": "The best things in life they are free",
      "translation": "那就是生命中最好的东西往往是免费的"
    },
    {
      "time": 74.044,
      "time_str": "01:14.044",
      "text": "But if you wanna cry",
      "translation": "但是如果你想要哭泣"
    },
    {
      "time": 76.864,
      "time_str": "01:16.864",
      "text": "Cry on my shoulder",
      "translation": "就靠着我的肩膀吧"
    },
    {
      "time": 80.146,
      "time_str": "01:20.146",
      "text": "If you need someone",
      "translation": "如果你想要一个人"
    },
    {
      "time": 82.801,
      "time_str": "01:22.801",
      "text": "Who cares for you",
      "translation": "来关心你"
    },
    {
      "time": 86.06,
      "time_str": "01:26.060",
      "text": "If you're feeling sad",
      "translation": "如果你感到悲伤"
    },
    {
      "time": 88.776,
      "time_str": "01:28.776",
      "text": "Your heart gets colder",
      "translation": "心灵也变得寒冷"
    },
    {
      "time": 93.519,
      "time_str": "01:33.519",
      "text": "Yes I show you what real love can do",
      "translation": "我会告诉你真正的爱的作用"
    },
    {
      "time": 103.581,
      "time_str": "01:43.581",
      "text": "If your sky is grey oh, let me know",
      "translation": "如果你的天空一片黑暗，请让我知晓"
    },
    {
      "time": 109.386,
      "time_str": "01:49.386",
      "text": "There's a place in heaven where we'll go",
      "translation": "我们要去的地方在天堂"
    },
    {
      "time": 115.382,
      "time_str": "01:55.382",
      "text": "If heaven is a million years away",
      "translation": "如果天堂在那百万年之外"
    },
    {
      "time": 120.947,
      "time_str": "02:00.947",
      "text": "Oh, just call me and I'll make your day",
      "translation": "那就来找我，我会让你开心"
    },
    {
      "time": 127.155,
      "time_str": "02:07.155",
      "text": "When the nights are gettin' cold and blue",
      "translation": "当夜晚变得越来越寒冷和令人悲伤"
    },
    {
      "time": 133.068,
      "time_str": "02:13.068",
      "text": "When the days are gettin' hard for you",
      "translation": "当生活变得越来越艰难"
    },
    {
      "time": 139.024,
      "time_str": "02:19.024",
      "text": "I will always stay here by your side",
      "translation": "我会一直陪在你身边"
    },
    {
      "time": 143.498,
      "time_str": "02:23.498",
      "text": "I promise you I'll never hide",
      "translation": "我保证我不会消失"
    },
    {
